<%#
# Text Form Partial

This partial renders a textarea element for a text attribute.

## Local variables:

- `f`:
  A Rails form generator, used to help create the appropriate input fields.
- `field`:
  An instance of [Administrate::Field::Text][1].
  A wrapper around the Text pulled from the database.

[1]: http://www.rubydoc.info/gems/administrate/Administrate/Field/Text
%>
<div class="relative">
  <%= f.label field.attribute, class: "font-medium text-gray-900" %>
  <%= f.text_area field.attribute, class: "block w-full px-4 py-3 mb-4 border border-2 border-transparent border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none" %>
</div>
